This paper deals with improving the quality of statistical machine translation by utilizing lexical resources. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques to improve machine translation, which makes it relevant to the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms to improve translation quality, which makes it relevant to the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques to improve the coverage and quality of machine translation, which makes it relevant to the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper involves the use of neural networks to improve machine translation, which makes it relevant to the category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
